name: InfluenzaTestsForInfluenzaAOrBVirusNucleicAcid
title: Influenza (Tests for influenza A or B virus Nucleic Acid)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes for lab test names to detect nucleic acids of Influenza A or B virus),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify laboratory tests names),(Inclusion Criteria: VSAC query: Influenza virus A or B nucleic acid;),(Exclusion Criteria: panel tests; isolate tests; donor tests)
